Aura of Cold, Lesser
Transmutation [Cold]
Level: Cleric 3, druid 3, paladin 4,
ranger 4
Components: V, S, DF
Casting Time: 1 standard action
Range: 5 ft.
Area: 5-ft.-radius spherical emanation,
centered on you
Duration: 1 round/level (D)
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: Yes

You are covered in a thin layer of
white frost and frigid cold emanates
from your body, dealing 1d6 points of
cold damage at the start of your round
to each creature within 5 feet.